Description: Refreshing and sensual, Intimately Yours for Men from David Beckham captivates your senses with its invigorating aroma. Inspired by the style and sophistication of the iconic footballer, the luxurious fragrance of this Eau de Toilette emanates an aura of glamour and sophistication. Created by perfumer Christophe Raynaud, the gourmand Oriental citrus scent of Intimately Yours opens with top note that mingles vibrant blood mandarin with crisp, crushed leaf and ice lemon. The fragrant heart note comprises of sage that has been fused with basil and lavender. An earthy, sensuous base note of sandalwood, tonka beans and the depth of vetiver imparts an essential warmth, a refined aura of masculinity to this signature scent. Encased in a vial that is reminiscent of contemporary architecture, the sparkling, clear hues of the essence hint at a purity, a thrill that only an intimate moment can grant. Create your own intimate moment with the enticing Intimately Yours.

Title: J. Del Pozo Halloween EDC  -  100 ml(For Women)
Description: Eccentric yet thrilling, this luxury scent accentuates the woman who personifies the bewildering duality of seduction and innocence. For the bewitching woman, J.Del Pozo Halloween celebrates her playful yet dark streak. Created by perfumer Max Gavarry of IFF, this entrancing Eau de Toilette is made for the eponymous house of J.Del Pozo. Piquing your interest from the first waft, the top note packs a killer combination of powdery soft hints of violet, earthy and refreshing green banana that is garnished with bright citrusy notes of green lime along with the refreshing and soothing essence of Alaskan seas. Evaporating into the heart, you are wrapped in a haze of lush and lemony magnolia, exotic hints of muguet, spicy notes of pepper, delicate tuberose with traces of atrezzo violet. It descends into a warm base note of rich sandalwood, aromatic notes of incense, creamy vanilla and resinous myrrh. An array of aromatic ingredients fuse together to produce an intoxicating floral oriental fragrance. With a spritz of this hypnotic perfume, transform your evenings into a carnival of whimsy and fancy. Poured into a crystal amphora bottle, this sensuous fragrance radiates a lovely shade of lavender. A silver aluminium base and top complete the mesmerising vial. Walk into the masquerade as the ravishing sorceress in an ethereal aura who has cast her spell on the night.

For the wise, contemporary man, who travels the globe and yet retains his playful nature, much like the jaguar - this luxury perfume is a symbol of performance and power. The unmistakable signature note of this Eau de Toilette adds an electrifying, sporty elegance. A luxurious and urbane concoction, Performance is a perfect blend of spicy notes with the subtlety of ambrosial lavender. Created by perfumer Harry Fremont, Performance opens with a fresh, minty top note of basil, mandarin, peppermint and cypress and trails into a heart of violet leaves, nutmeg, sage and geranium. The warm base note of tonka beans, tropical woods and velvety white musk adds a touch of exotic opulence. Perfect for a romantic night out, Performance delights with its subtle, sensual notes that are essentially masculine.

Description: Mysterious, enigmatic and provocative, the scent of Polo Black from the fashion house of Ralph Lauren stands out through its complex versatility. A confluence of elegant woody aromatic accords, this Eau de Toilette defines the charismatic charm of a gentleman through its elegant, gourmand notes.
